WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.730
Happy New Year

3
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.540
Oh, really? So you're keeping 
the status quo with Hananoi-kun?

4
00:00:07.540 --> 00:00:09.730
A-As embarrassing as it is, yeah.

5
00:00:10.180 --> 00:00:14.820
If I'd known, I wouldn't have asked 
you to come in a big group.

6
00:00:14.820 --> 00:00:17.250
But Hananoi-kun said he'd come too.

7
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:22.160
And I'd like it if you guys can 
all become friends with him too!

8
00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:23.950
<i>I'm sorry, Hananoi-kun!</i>

9
00:00:24.380 --> 00:00:26.240
Hotaru! Hibiki!

10
00:00:26.860 --> 00:00:28.240
Happy New Year!

11
00:00:29.130 --> 00:00:30.560
Happy New Year!

12
00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:32.610
Now we just gotta wait for the boys.

13
00:00:32.610 --> 00:00:35.150
Oh, I bet Hananoi-kun is already here.

14
00:00:35.850 --> 00:00:38.020
He always shows up way early for stuff,

15
00:00:38.020 --> 00:00:40.920
so I've been asking him 
to wait somewhere warm.

16
00:00:42.340 --> 00:00:43.640
Hananoi-kun!

17
00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:45.770
Hotaru-chan!

18
00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:48.470
Happy New Year.

19
00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:49.930
Haven't seen you since Christmas.

20
00:00:52.290 --> 00:00:54.860
<i>Huh? Wh-What is this?</i>

21
00:00:56.150 --> 00:01:01.900
<i>Hananoi-kun is more radiant than usual today.</i>

22
00:00:56.200 --> 00:01:00.940
Thanks for the New Year's card. 
Let's make it a great year, okay?

23
00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.140
Hotaru-chan?

24
00:01:04.140 --> 00:01:06.570
Oh! Let me introduce my friends.

25
00:01:06.570 --> 00:01:09.450
This is Kyo-chan and Shibamu.
We're all in the same class.

26
00:01:09.450 --> 00:01:10.940
H-Hello!

27
00:01:10.940 --> 00:01:12.390
I'm Asami Hibiki.

28
00:01:12.390 --> 00:01:14.050
I'm Shibamura Tsukiha.

29
00:01:14.370 --> 00:01:17.170
Kyo-chan and I were classmates
in middle school, too.

30
00:01:17.420 --> 00:01:20.970
I feel kinda bad for making 
you come with all of us.

31
00:01:20.970 --> 00:01:22.560
I bet you two wanted to be alone.

32
00:01:24.100 --> 00:01:26.550
<i>Maybe it's me, but he 
doesn't look like he's laughing!</i>

33
00:01:26.930 --> 00:01:28.690
Mornin'!

34
00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.880
My bad. Sorry I'm late.

35
00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:32.440
Oh, Hananoi!

36
00:01:34.220 --> 00:01:36.080
Good to see you, man.

37
00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:38.230
Who are you?

38
00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:39.320
Uh?

39
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.800
Dude, we're in the same class!

40
00:03:14.290 --> 00:03:20.380
Episode 4

41
00:03:14.290 --> 00:03:20.380
Our First Shrine Visit

42
00:03:16.760 --> 00:03:20.880
Wow! I know it gets this way
every year, but it sure is crowded!

43
00:03:21.230 --> 00:03:24.150
Hey, guys! Don't get separated, okay?

44
00:03:26.130 --> 00:03:27.470
Hotaru-chan.

45
00:03:28.980 --> 00:03:30.160
If it's okay with you...

46
00:03:31.720 --> 00:03:33.740
I-I'm good!

47
00:03:34.660 --> 00:03:36.710
I'll hang on to Shibamu.

48
00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:38.140
Oh, fine by me.

49
00:03:38.140 --> 00:03:39.240
Why not take my arm?

50
00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:42.360
Ooh, you feel so stable!

51
00:03:45.740 --> 00:03:50.440
<i>I hope that all of my friends 
are happy every day</i>

52
00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:53.850
<i>and that I can learn what love is.</i>

53
00:03:55.770 --> 00:03:58.110
My wish only took a second.

54
00:03:58.110 --> 00:03:59.810
Don't you want to ask for something?

55
00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:03.680
God has never really done anything for me.

56
00:04:04.090 --> 00:04:07.010
<i>Oh... really?</i>

57
00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:11.330
Cool. That's wishes down, so let's go eat.

58
00:04:11.330 --> 00:04:14.190
What? Let's draw our fortunes first.

59
00:04:14.190 --> 00:04:16.440
Charms

60
00:04:14.190 --> 00:04:16.440
Fortunes

61
00:04:14.190 --> 00:04:16.450
But the lines are huge right now.

62
00:04:16.750 --> 00:04:19.060
Right? Don't you think so, Hinase-san?

63
00:04:19.060 --> 00:04:20.450
Huh? Actually, I...

64
00:04:26.440 --> 00:04:29.060
Okay. You guys are in charge of mains and sides.

65
00:04:29.060 --> 00:04:32.010
We'll take care of drinks and dessert.

66
00:04:32.010 --> 00:04:33.690
We'll meet up at the torii gate!

67
00:04:33.690 --> 00:04:34.870
All right!

68
00:04:36.290 --> 00:04:39.830
Okay, what should we go for?

69
00:04:40.460 --> 00:04:43.220
Hey. What do you wanna eat, Hananoi?

70
00:04:44.190 --> 00:04:48.570
Jeez, man, I can tell you're
head over heels for Hinase-san.

71
00:04:48.570 --> 00:04:52.110
You don't act anything like that at school.
Color me surprised.

72
00:04:52.430 --> 00:04:56.420
Why not share some of that
sunshine with your classmates?

73
00:04:58.350 --> 00:05:00.900
I have no intention of becoming friends.

74
00:05:00.900 --> 00:05:01.690
Huh?

75
00:05:02.660 --> 00:05:03.530
Wh-What?

76
00:05:04.970 --> 00:05:06.020
It was you, right?

77
00:05:06.580 --> 00:05:10.700
Who filled Hotaru's head with ideas 
of trying out kissing and stuff.

78
00:05:11.830 --> 00:05:15.620
Honestly, this whole thing today 
is kind of a pain in the ass.

79
00:05:16.270 --> 00:05:19.120
I don't have "sunshine" to share
with anyone but Hotaru-chan.

80
00:05:21.290 --> 00:05:23.410
So if you get it, stay out of my way, okay?

81
00:05:24.530 --> 00:05:26.950
I wonder if the boys are getting along.

82
00:05:27.250 --> 00:05:30.010
They're classmates. I'm sure they're fine.

83
00:05:27.260 --> 00:05:30.010
Yakisoba

84
00:05:27.260 --> 00:05:30.010
Baby Castella

85
00:05:27.260 --> 00:05:30.010
Grilled

86
00:05:27.260 --> 00:05:30.010
Squid

87
00:05:30.010 --> 00:05:33.750
But Hananoi-kun doesn't really
 seem to be feeling it today.

88
00:05:33.750 --> 00:05:34.840
Huh?

89
00:05:34.840 --> 00:05:36.760
You didn't even notice?!

90
00:05:36.760 --> 00:05:39.360
He hasn't talked to anyone but you, Hotaru.

91
00:05:39.940 --> 00:05:41.840
I had no idea...

92
00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:44.440
Well, you haven't seen each other recently.

93
00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:47.370
Of course he wants to be alone
with the girl he likes.

94
00:05:47.770 --> 00:05:50.280
But, I mean, it's only been a week.

95
00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:52.530
You <i>really</i> don't get it!

96
00:05:52.530 --> 00:05:55.150
When you're in love, even a day
apart feels like eternity!

97
00:05:55.150 --> 00:05:57.290
Love makes every day together sparkle!

98
00:05:57.640 --> 00:06:00.060
D-Do you agree, Shibamu?

99
00:06:00.060 --> 00:06:02.820
Yeah, I guess so.

100
00:06:02.820 --> 00:06:06.550
When you've waited to see someone, 
it's great to finally reunite.

101
00:06:06.930 --> 00:06:09.010
I know what that feels like.

102
00:06:15.960 --> 00:06:17.980
What's wrong, Hotaru?

103
00:06:18.690 --> 00:06:21.070
I almost feel like we're having girl talk.

104
00:06:21.070 --> 00:06:22.790
This is 100 percent girl talk!

105
00:06:22.790 --> 00:06:25.990
You're totally out of your element,
aren't you, Hotaru?

106
00:06:26.730 --> 00:06:28.120
Hey!

107
00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:31.410
Wait, where's Hananoi-kun?

108
00:06:31.410 --> 00:06:32.340
Huh?

109
00:06:32.340 --> 00:06:36.760
Um... On the way, yeah, we got split up.

110
00:06:37.010 --> 00:06:39.820
But he knows where we're meeting,
so I'm sure it's fine.

111
00:06:41.950 --> 00:06:44.480
I'm gonna go look around.

112
00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:45.960
You can eat without me!

113
00:06:51.250 --> 00:06:51.960
Oh!

114
00:06:55.030 --> 00:06:56.320
Hananoi-kun!

115
00:06:57.550 --> 00:06:58.950
Hotaru-chan.

116
00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:05.230
Well then, thank you very 
much for your help.

117
00:07:05.230 --> 00:07:07.350
Not at all. Please take care.

118
00:07:05.230 --> 00:07:15.240
Grilled Squid

119
00:07:07.810 --> 00:07:09.140
Someone you know?

120
00:07:09.140 --> 00:07:12.170
No. I just happened to be
there to lend a hand.

121
00:07:12.170 --> 00:07:15.240
Sorry. I was about to head back.

122
00:07:17.750 --> 00:07:18.920
Hotaru-chan?

123
00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:22.630
I-It's nothing. Let's catch up with everyone.

124
00:07:25.040 --> 00:07:25.960
Wait.

125
00:07:27.960 --> 00:07:32.470
Buttered Potatoes

126
00:07:28.710 --> 00:07:31.830
Can we stay just the two of us
 a little longer?

127
00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:41.530
It's been so long since 
we got to talk like this.

128
00:07:41.530 --> 00:07:43.410
Yeah, you're right.

129
00:07:43.810 --> 00:07:46.980
I'm sorry I couldn't spend 
New Year's with you.

130
00:07:47.450 --> 00:07:50.910
My little sister was in a tizzy
on New Year's Eve.

131
00:07:50.910 --> 00:07:53.690
You like your stupid boyfriend 
more than me!

132
00:07:55.560 --> 00:08:01.130
With your family and all your friends, 
it's gonna be tough to get you all to myself.

133
00:08:02.190 --> 00:08:06.460
<i>But Hananoi-kun doesn't really
 seem to be feeling it today.</i>

134
00:08:06.930 --> 00:08:09.640
Um, are you having fun?

135
00:08:09.990 --> 00:08:13.760
As long as you're with me, 
Hotaru-chan, I'm happy anywhere.

136
00:08:13.760 --> 00:08:17.960
U-Um, Kyo-chan and Shibamu 
are both really nice.

137
00:08:19.140 --> 00:08:20.380
I'm sure they are.

138
00:08:20.810 --> 00:08:25.490
If you like them, Hotaru-chan, 
I'm sure they're great people.

139
00:08:25.490 --> 00:08:27.980
<i>Ah, this mood...</i>

140
00:08:29.270 --> 00:08:33.230
<i>I wonder if I misunderstood 
how Hananoi-kun feels again.</i>

141
00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:37.990
<i>I really wish he could make
friends with Kyo-chan and the others,</i>

142
00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:40.650
<i>but I guess I shouldn't try to force it.</i>

143
00:08:40.650 --> 00:08:41.700
Oh!

144
00:08:41.700 --> 00:08:45.360
Uh, sorry. There was a 
leaf stuck in your hair.

145
00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:47.390
O-Oh...

146
00:08:50.920 --> 00:08:54.230
Hotaru-chan, are you avoiding me today?

147
00:08:54.230 --> 00:08:57.180
Huh? Oh, no! I'm not avoiding you.

148
00:08:57.180 --> 00:09:00.180
I just, I don't know, feel a little shy.

149
00:09:00.660 --> 00:09:04.450
Maybe because we haven't seen each 
other recently? I wonder why.

150
00:09:04.450 --> 00:09:06.580
I don't really understand it myself.

151
00:09:08.820 --> 00:09:10.200
Okay.

152
00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:12.060
Maybe we're making some progress then.

153
00:09:12.500 --> 00:09:13.240
Huh?

154
00:09:15.490 --> 00:09:21.490
Um, listen, would you let me 
recharge just for a little bit?

155
00:09:22.380 --> 00:09:23.200
Oh.

156
00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:26.750
Is your phone battery running low?

157
00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:31.240
W-Wait, h-huh? What did you mean?

158
00:09:31.910 --> 00:09:33.120
Don't worry.

159
00:09:33.670 --> 00:09:35.420
Just stay right there.

160
00:09:36.170 --> 00:09:38.140
I promise not to touch you.

161
00:09:41.170 --> 00:09:43.130
I haven't had enough of you recently.

162
00:09:44.090 --> 00:09:45.610
I thought I was going to die.

163
00:09:48.510 --> 00:09:51.830
<i>Wh-What am I supposed to do?</i>

164
00:09:54.500 --> 00:09:57.200
<i>I can smell Hananoi-kun...</i>

165
00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:04.880
<i>It's been a while since he's 
been this close to me.</i>

166
00:10:15.900 --> 00:10:21.140
<i>I feel kind of nervous, but I also feel 
like I'm getting something that I needed.</i>

167
00:10:22.750 --> 00:10:26.380
<i>Could that mean I wanted to see him too?</i>

168
00:10:27.740 --> 00:10:29.150
Thank you.

169
00:10:33.940 --> 00:10:35.520
All charged up now.

170
00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.400
Want to go back to the others?

171
00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:39.530
Yeah.

172
00:10:40.420 --> 00:10:41.790
<i>So that's it.</i>

173
00:10:42.570 --> 00:10:44.690
<i>That's what he meant by a "recharge."</i>

174
00:10:47.330 --> 00:10:54.170
<i>I'm learning new things every day,
but there's still so much I don't understand.</i>

175
00:10:54.810 --> 00:11:00.170
<i>I want to discover even more. 
Like what kind of person Hananoi-kun is.</i>

176
00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:05.110
<i>What he cares about. What he treasures.</i>

177
00:11:05.720 --> 00:11:11.590
<i>And then someday, I want to put
the biggest smile on his face.</i>

178
00:11:13.640 --> 00:11:15.140
<i>I'd like to see that.</i>

179
00:11:16.690 --> 00:11:18.690
Charms

180
00:11:16.690 --> 00:11:18.690
Fortunes

181
00:11:30.910 --> 00:11:32.580
Is this spot okay?

182
00:11:38.880 --> 00:11:43.640
<u>Your Wish</u>
It may take time, but it will eventually come true.
<u>The Person You're Waiting For</u>
They may be late to arrive.
 <u>The Thing You've Lost</u>
 Take your time looking for it.
 <u>Your Journey</u>
 A place close to the sea is best.

183
00:11:41.210 --> 00:11:42.290
<i>Someday...</i>

184
00:11:47.560 --> 00:11:48.640
Huh?

185
00:11:48.640 --> 00:11:50.450
Hey, Yao!

186
00:11:50.450 --> 00:11:51.770
Oh, sorry.

187
00:11:51.770 --> 00:11:52.690
What's up?

188
00:11:53.050 --> 00:11:57.430
Nothing. I just thought 
I saw a familiar face.

189
00:12:04.310 --> 00:12:05.960
Welcome!

190
00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:08.590
<i>It's the third term now.</i>

191
00:12:08.590 --> 00:12:09.940
Thank you very much.

192
00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:12.450
<i>I decided to get a part-time job 
for a change of pace.</i>

193
00:12:12.860 --> 00:12:15.830
Hota-chan, you've already 
gotten the hang of checkout!

194
00:12:16.310 --> 00:12:18.330
S-Satomura-san...

195
00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:20.770
<i>After the other day,</i>

196
00:12:20.770 --> 00:12:25.690
<i>I was reminded just how much
I don't know about Hananoi-kun,</i>

197
00:12:25.690 --> 00:12:31.720
<i>so I decided to step into a world 
I think interests him.</i>

198
00:12:32.060 --> 00:12:33.220
Excuse me!

199
00:12:33.610 --> 00:12:34.920
Coming!

200
00:12:37.990 --> 00:12:41.970
<i>This is my first job and everything 
about it makes me nervous.</i>

201
00:12:41.970 --> 00:12:43.200
Excuse me.

202
00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:45.350
Yes! Welcome...

203
00:12:45.810 --> 00:12:47.100
I'd like to buy these.

204
00:12:47.100 --> 00:12:50.280
Hananoi-kun! You really came to see me!

205
00:12:50.280 --> 00:12:50.980
Yeah!

206
00:12:51.750 --> 00:12:55.040
Black Hole Traveler

207
00:12:52.490 --> 00:12:54.420
You look good in the uniform.

208
00:12:55.390 --> 00:12:56.980
Can I take a picture later?

209
00:12:56.980 --> 00:12:59.510
D-Don't tease me!

210
00:12:59.510 --> 00:13:01.300
For these two items,
your total is 1,100 yen.

211
00:13:02.250 --> 00:13:05.670
<i>Since school's started back up 
and I see him every day,</i>

212
00:13:05.670 --> 00:13:09.810
<i>I don't get flustered each time
we meet up like I used to.</i>

213
00:13:10.180 --> 00:13:14.690
Kohdansha Novel Awards SciFi Winner

214
00:13:10.700 --> 00:13:13.200
I didn't know you read books like these.

215
00:13:13.200 --> 00:13:14.680
I read everything.

216
00:13:15.850 --> 00:13:19.450
<i>Deciding to work here is already paying off!</i>

217
00:13:19.900 --> 00:13:22.830
Say, Hotaru-chan, how late 
are you working today?

218
00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:25.770
I'm on until closing, so eight.

219
00:13:26.100 --> 00:13:28.970
Okay. Can I wait over 
there until you're done?

220
00:13:28.970 --> 00:13:32.510
Huh? Th-That's fine, but it's only six right now.

221
00:13:32.990 --> 00:13:34.830
I'll read while I wait.

222
00:13:36.950 --> 00:13:38.460
See you then, okay?

223
00:13:39.950 --> 00:13:41.330
Hey, hey!

224
00:13:41.330 --> 00:13:44.340
I-Is that guy a friend of yours?

225
00:13:44.340 --> 00:13:46.800
Oh, um, yeah. We go to the same school.

226
00:13:47.150 --> 00:13:51.310
Oh wow! He's so good-looking!

227
00:13:54.840 --> 00:13:56.320
What a surprise.

228
00:13:56.920 --> 00:14:00.160
I always figured you'd 
get a job at a restaurant.

229
00:14:00.600 --> 00:14:02.190
Why did you pick a bookstore?

230
00:14:02.190 --> 00:14:04.940
Um, well...

231
00:14:09.970 --> 00:14:12.830
N-No particular reason!

232
00:14:12.830 --> 00:14:15.050
Oh, okay.

233
00:14:15.050 --> 00:14:18.070
<i>Oh no! That must have come off wrong.</i>

234
00:14:18.340 --> 00:14:23.840
<i>What is this? I feel like I'm obsessing
over his reactions recently.</i>

235
00:14:23.840 --> 00:14:25.310
Working part-time, huh?

236
00:14:26.320 --> 00:14:29.530
I'll be disappointed if this
means less time together.

237
00:14:29.970 --> 00:14:33.340
Don't worry! It's only three days a week.

238
00:14:33.340 --> 00:14:34.630
I guess so.

239
00:14:35.720 --> 00:14:38.690
Several Days Later...

240
00:14:36.470 --> 00:14:38.290
Have a good night!

241
00:14:39.920 --> 00:14:40.720
Huh?

242
00:14:41.610 --> 00:14:43.080
Hananoi-kun?

243
00:14:45.790 --> 00:14:47.680
Were you waiting for me?

244
00:14:47.680 --> 00:14:51.440
Yeah. I was just leaving the 
library and noticed the time.

245
00:14:51.990 --> 00:14:53.730
It's already dark, so I'll walk you home.

246
00:14:55.870 --> 00:14:57.870
Several More Days Later...

247
00:14:57.930 --> 00:14:59.700
Have a good night!

248
00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:02.350
<i>Huh? Again?!</i>

249
00:15:02.350 --> 00:15:04.690
It's dangerous to be out alone at night.

250
00:15:04.690 --> 00:15:07.590
Night? But it isn't even six yet.

251
00:15:07.940 --> 00:15:10.350
Hananoi-kun, I'll be okay by my—

252
00:15:10.930 --> 00:15:12.840
<i>Wait, no.</i>

253
00:15:13.130 --> 00:15:14.400
<i>That's right.</i>

254
00:15:15.200 --> 00:15:20.860
<i>Hananoi-kun values our time 
together more than I realize.</i>

255
00:15:22.270 --> 00:15:24.850
Actually, sure. If it's okay with you.

256
00:15:28.760 --> 00:15:32.030
<i>Wow! He looks so happy.</i>

257
00:15:32.730 --> 00:15:37.780
<i>We respond to things differently,
so I'll have to be mindful.</i>

258
00:15:38.390 --> 00:15:42.770
<i>I think once I figure that out, I'll start 
to understand who Hananoi-kun is inside.</i>

259
00:15:44.210 --> 00:15:45.050
Oh.

260
00:15:45.050 --> 00:15:47.010
Huh?! Big Sis?!

261
00:15:48.340 --> 00:15:50.660
You said you had work today!

262
00:15:50.660 --> 00:15:52.330
Yeah, I just got off.

263
00:15:52.800 --> 00:15:54.890
He walked me home because it's dark.

264
00:15:55.260 --> 00:15:58.340
My! Thank you, Hananoi-kun!

265
00:15:58.660 --> 00:16:00.740
I'll be on my way.

266
00:16:00.740 --> 00:16:02.110
Oh, already?

267
00:16:02.110 --> 00:16:05.680
Why not stay for dinner 
since you came all this way?

268
00:16:14.350 --> 00:16:16.260
Hananoi-kun, thanks for waiting!

269
00:16:17.310 --> 00:16:19.730
Dinner will be ready in a little bit.

270
00:16:23.770 --> 00:16:28.040
Um, I know I promised not to touch you,

271
00:16:28.040 --> 00:16:32.500
but in a situation like this, Hotaru-chan, 
you shouldn't let your guard down.

272
00:16:32.810 --> 00:16:34.770
Oh, uh, right!

273
00:16:35.370 --> 00:16:40.690
<i>My only thought was spending time
together since he's been so lonely.</i>

274
00:16:41.170 --> 00:16:45.530
<i>He's kept his distance
since he "recharged," but...</i>

275
00:16:45.970 --> 00:16:49.780
Oh, that's right, Hotaru-chan. 
It's my turn, isn't it?

276
00:16:52.010 --> 00:16:53.400
Thanks!

277
00:16:53.400 --> 00:16:56.090
I actually just wrote in it a few minutes ago.

278
00:16:56.090 --> 00:16:56.730
Huh?

279
00:16:57.780 --> 00:17:00.290
I want to see what little Hotaru-chan looked like

280
00:17:00.750 --> 00:17:02.660
Wow!

281
00:17:04.120 --> 00:17:07.440
S-So cute!

282
00:17:09.750 --> 00:17:12.680
N-Next time, you have to show 
me your photo albums too!

283
00:17:13.170 --> 00:17:13.970
Huh?

284
00:17:14.370 --> 00:17:16.730
I don't think they'd be very interesting.

285
00:17:16.730 --> 00:17:18.100
<i>Look who's talking!</i>

286
00:17:18.710 --> 00:17:22.540
I was boring and nerdy when I was a kid.

287
00:17:22.540 --> 00:17:25.580
Really? I can't even imagine that.

288
00:17:25.580 --> 00:17:28.440
<i>This is my chance to ask him things!</i>

289
00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:30.610
Oh...

290
00:17:31.470 --> 00:17:34.600
U-Um, Hananoi-kun, when you were younger—

291
00:17:34.600 --> 00:17:37.520
Hotaru-chan, you look good 
even with long hair.

292
00:17:44.130 --> 00:17:47.280
Would you ever grow it out again?

293
00:17:48.100 --> 00:17:48.940
Ah...

294
00:17:50.180 --> 00:17:51.240
My hair?

295
00:17:53.230 --> 00:17:58.540
No... I, uh... I don't think I ever will.

296
00:18:01.560 --> 00:18:04.310
<i>Crap! I'm making things awkward again!</i>

297
00:18:04.770 --> 00:18:07.570
What about you, Hananoi-kun?

298
00:18:07.570 --> 00:18:11.200
I thought you looked nice with 
long hair when we first met.

299
00:18:11.770 --> 00:18:15.060
In that case, maybe I'll grow it out.

300
00:18:15.450 --> 00:18:18.330
You'd go back to that?

301
00:18:21.160 --> 00:18:22.160
<i>Wait...</i>

302
00:18:23.300 --> 00:18:26.740
<i>I keep doing the same thing recently.</i>

303
00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:31.050
<i>Is it okay to just let that go?</i>

304
00:18:31.570 --> 00:18:36.240
<i>I want to ask Hananoi-kun more,
 but I'm not talking about myself.</i>

305
00:18:37.290 --> 00:18:38.560
<i>Is that okay?</i>

306
00:18:41.600 --> 00:18:43.590
U-Um, you know what?

307
00:18:43.940 --> 00:18:45.040
Hmm?

308
00:18:45.040 --> 00:18:51.780
The reason I wanted to work at a bookstore 
is because I wanted to understand you better.

309
00:18:51.780 --> 00:18:52.400
Huh?

310
00:18:52.800 --> 00:18:58.770
And also, well, a long time ago,
someone cut my hair as a prank.

311
00:18:58.770 --> 00:19:00.860
It was back in elementary school.

312
00:19:01.300 --> 00:19:06.200
A friend I used to be really close with
 did it as a joke.

313
00:19:06.640 --> 00:19:08.370
It was a real shock.

314
00:19:09.330 --> 00:19:12.830
And since then, I've kept my hair short.

315
00:19:12.830 --> 00:19:16.290
Is that the friend you mentioned before
that you fell out with?

316
00:19:16.290 --> 00:19:17.580
Yeah.

317
00:19:17.580 --> 00:19:23.050
I hurt her first,
and I didn't realize how badly.

318
00:19:23.660 --> 00:19:27.130
So we're kind of even, I guess.

319
00:19:27.570 --> 00:19:33.140
I've been terrible about understanding 
people's feelings since I was little.

320
00:19:34.410 --> 00:19:35.660
<i>I said it.</i>

321
00:19:39.650 --> 00:19:41.310
<i>Maybe that was too heavy.</i>

322
00:19:42.280 --> 00:19:43.610
In my case,

323
00:19:44.800 --> 00:19:47.770
I was a gloomy kid in elementary school.

324
00:19:47.770 --> 00:19:51.410
I was too scared to talk 
to people I didn't know.

325
00:19:51.970 --> 00:19:53.780
<i>You</i> were, Hananoi-kun?

326
00:19:53.780 --> 00:19:56.700
I transferred partway 
through elementary school,

327
00:19:56.700 --> 00:20:00.200
but I couldn't make a single friend
 at my new school either.

328
00:20:00.200 --> 00:20:01.880
I was really the worst.

329
00:20:03.990 --> 00:20:06.530
Then we're two of a kind.

330
00:20:09.360 --> 00:20:11.830
<i>Hananoi-kun is so nice.</i>

331
00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:16.450
<i>I'm glad I told him. That's the first 
time he's opened up about his past.</i>

332
00:20:17.190 --> 00:20:18.940
I'm so glad you told me.

333
00:20:19.740 --> 00:20:20.840
Thank you.

334
00:20:21.270 --> 00:20:23.100
That must have been hard to share.

335
00:20:24.760 --> 00:20:27.580
Hotaru-chan, there's
nothing terrible about you.

336
00:20:28.340 --> 00:20:31.890
Nobody can truly understand 
the hearts of others,

337
00:20:31.890 --> 00:20:36.190
and yet you still try to understand me.

338
00:20:36.810 --> 00:20:40.330
You think about how I feel. You try so hard.

339
00:20:41.180 --> 00:20:44.960
With you, Hotaru-chan,
I'm experiencing so much for the first time.

340
00:20:49.760 --> 00:20:51.100
<i>We're the same.</i>

341
00:20:51.770 --> 00:20:54.580
<i>I'm not the only one who 
gets overwhelmed by new things</i>

342
00:20:54.580 --> 00:20:56.440
<i>and wants to learn more.</i>

343
00:20:57.120 --> 00:20:59.120
<i>It isn't just me.</i>

344
00:21:08.500 --> 00:21:10.490
I-I'm sorry! I mean...

345
00:21:17.990 --> 00:21:23.120
I-I-I-I-I'm really sorry! Your head was 
in the perfect spot, so I just...

346
00:21:24.020 --> 00:21:24.770
Hota—

347
00:21:24.770 --> 00:21:28.410
Hotaru, Hananoi-kun! Dinner's ready!

348
00:21:37.850 --> 00:21:42.810
<i>Why did I do that? I know Hananoi-kun 
is trying to hold back.</i>

349
00:21:43.500 --> 00:21:50.290
<i>For some reason, I just suddenly 
wanted to touch him so badly.</i>

350
00:21:52.430 --> 00:21:55.380
Well, thanks for dinner.

351
00:21:55.380 --> 00:21:56.830
See you tomorrow!

352
00:21:59.580 --> 00:22:02.340
What's wrong with me?

353
00:22:02.850 --> 00:22:07.850
